-Martin.

03:43.640 --> 03:45.000
We are peaceful people.

03:47.040 --> 03:48.040
How can I be sure?

03:48.120 --> 03:50.960
You can't, but you can choose
to believe me.

03:53.560 --> 03:55.240
Don't give them your gun, Martin.

03:56.000 --> 03:59.000
