We need to get inside.

04:20.800 --> 04:23.640
Come on. Come on in.

04:27.920 --> 04:29.120
Come on in.

04:38.320 --> 04:39.520
What is this place?

04:40.880 --> 04:43.920
All you need to know
is that once you enter...

04:44.920 --> 04:46.360
