08:12.000 --> 08:14.640
Well, how else would you shower?

08:15.160 --> 08:16.720
Don't worry.

08:16.800 --> 08:19.320
We have our own well,
and we clean the water.

08:19.880 --> 08:22.000
Nothing here is dangerous.

08:22.080 --> 08:23.920
-Like the tomatoes?
-Precisely.

08:24.000 --> 08:25.560
Just like the tomatoes.

08:25.640 --> 08:26.520
Okay.

