19:18.000 --> 19:20.880
Yes, a doctor stitched him up...

19:20.960 --> 19:23.640
I don't want to know anything
about the past.

19:26.320 --> 19:27.560
What about the pills?

19:28.320 --> 19:31.160
-You're not having any more pills.
-But it really hurts.

19:36.600 --> 19:38.280
