19:40.040 --> 19:45.440
We're out of antibiotics.
You need to rest for at least a week.

19:52.160 --> 19:53.800
Wait. No, thanks.

19:54.520 --> 19:55.520
No sedative.

19:56.120 --> 19:56.960
