21:40.840 --> 21:42.200
Who are you?

21:44.000 --> 21:47.080
Who are you? Are you connected to Apollon?

21:48.360 --> 21:50.320
That belongs to the past.

21:50.400 --> 21:51.240
This...

21:53.360 --> 21:54.200
You had this.

21:55.360 --> 21:57.080
-Yes.
-What is it?

21:58.800 --> 22:00.160
A sedative. I told you.

22:00.240 --> 22:01.800
A sedative?

22:04.400 --> 22:05.880
