22:14.680 --> 22:16.640
-No.
-I'll take that.

22:16.960 --> 22:18.200
No, you don't.

22:18.280 --> 22:19.400
Give it to me.

22:19.480 --> 22:20.800
-What?
-No, don't.

22:20.880 --> 22:24.280
-Don't do that. Put it away.
-Why?

22:24.360 --> 22:26.520
-You can kill us all with that.
-What? Why?

22:26.600 --> 22:29.040
-Why did you bring it here?
-Tell me what's in it.

22:30.280 --> 22:33.040
