22:38.080 --> 22:41.200
I just want to know what's in it.

22:42.240 --> 22:44.800
Believe me... you don't.

22:54.080 --> 22:55.760
You understand, don't you?

22:56.520 --> 22:59.480
That we have to free ourselves
of the past.

23:00.800 --> 23:02.360
