You don't know what I've done.

23:43.840 --> 23:46.480
Let it out.

23:48.120 --> 23:50.040
Let it go.

23:53.120 --> 23:54.600
Let go of it.

23:58.280 --> 23:59.560
Lea, you came.

23:59.640 --> 24:00.800
I did.

24:02.240 --> 24:03.080
Hi.

24:04.440 --> 24:05.840
Nice dress.

24:05.920 --> 24:06.840
Thanks.

24:13.400 --> 24:16.240
-Everybody is so pleased that you came.
-Really?

24:16.320 --> 24:17.800
Yes, they are so pleased.

24:18.240 --> 24:20.920
Great. I wasn't sure.

24:21.000 --> 24:23.120
-Here's your Coke.
-Thanks.

24:23.840 --> 24:26.120
-Thanks for inviting me.
-Sure.

24:34.480 --> 24:35.800
